title: Running Mix 2020 | 135 - 160 BPM | Best Running Music
description:
In many countries the complete lockdowns due to COVID-19 are being lifted, which in many cases means we can finally go back out to work out again! One of our favorite attributes to a good run is listening to some good music and that’s why we’ve made this mix! This mix is perfect for the more advanced runners who run at a higher tempo. Enjoy!
